title: #288: Death of a Salesman (@TimJDillon)
itunes:title: Death of a Salesman with Tim Dillon
description: Tim Dillon came to my apartment to tell me about his former life in sales. He's sold everything. From mortgages to office equipment to a history of New York. Tim has hilarious stories about all of it. Fun, fun, fun podcast.
